dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Columbia County, WI 2022
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways(ROW) for Columbia County, Wisconsin in 2022 and includes the layers 'COLUMBIA_ROADS_2022' and 'COLUMBIA_ROW_2022'
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://www.co.columbia.wi.us/columbiacounty/landinformation/LandInformation/tabid/757/Default.aspx]
